### Set Barber Availability - Monday
POST http://localhost:8080/api/barber-availability
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "barberId": 1,
  "dayOfWeek": "MONDAY",
  "startTime": "09:00",
  "endTime": "17:00",
  "isAvailable": true
}

